      • registerGlobalProperties

        public void registerGlobalProperties(AnalyticsProperties properties)
        Description copied from interface: AnalyticsCategoryBehavior
        Register properties that will be recorded by all the subsequent calls to AnalyticsCategoryBehavior.recordEvent(AnalyticsEventBehavior). AnalyticsProperties registered here can be overridden by passing the same name when calling `recordEvent`.

        Examples of global properties would be `selectedPlan`, `campaignSource`

        properties - Map of global properties wrapped as an instance of AnalyticsProperties
